{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a "Footwear Picks" product showcase section for ONE9 Shopify store, 
    fully admin-editable and with premium hover animations.
    
    SECTION STRUCTURE (Admin-Editable via Shopify Theme Editor):
    - Section title: "FOOTWEAR PICKS" (editable text field)
    - "VIEW ALL" link top-right, gold color (#F4C430), links to a collection 
      (editable URL/collection picker)
    - Product cards: use Shopify's native product picker block (not hardcoded), 
      so admin can select any product from inventory and it auto-pulls:
      - Product image (featured image)
      - Product title
      - Price (from variant, live-synced — NEVER hardcoded)
      - Color swatch (from variant metafield/option, auto-populated)
    - Number of cards: admin should be able to add/remove cards (2-4 recommended), 
      using Shopify block repeater pattern
    
    CARD LAYOUT (per product):
    - Background: #111111, rounded corners (12px), thin border (#2A2A2A, 1px)
    - Product image: centered, ~65% of card height, transparent/dark background 
      blending with card
    - Below image: product title (white, bold, 16px, 2-line max with ellipsis overflow)
    - Price: gold (#F4C430), bold, 15px, directly below title
    - Color swatch: small circle (14px), positioned below price, outlined border, 
      filled with actual product color (from swatch/variant data)
    - Card padding: 20px all sides
    
    HOVER ANIMATION (premium showcase effect):
    1. On card hover:
       - Card background lightens slightly (#111111 → #1A1A1A), transition 0.3s ease
       - Border color shifts from #2A2A2A → gold (#F4C430) at 40% opacity
       - Subtle gold glow appears around card edge: 
         box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(244, 196, 48, 0.15)
       - Product image scales up slightly: transform: scale(1.05), 
         transition 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1)
       - Product image gets a subtle upward float: translateY(-6px) combined with scale
    2. On price hover/card hover:
       - Price text gets soft gold text-shadow glow: 
         text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(244,196,48,0.6)
    3. Color swatch on hover:
       - Scale up 1.15x with ring/glow outline in gold
    
    QUICK-ADD INTERACTION (optional, best UX practice):
    - On card hover, reveal a small "Quick View" or "Add to Cart" pill button 
      that fades/slides up from bottom of image area
    - Button style: gold fill, black text, rounded, small (matches SHOP NOW CTA style)
    
    RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:
    - Desktop: 2-4 column grid (based on admin block count)
    - Mobile: horizontal scroll-snap carousel, cards ~160px width, 
      partial next-card peek for scroll affordance
    
    ADMIN CONTROLS TO EXPOSE IN SCHEMA:
    - Section heading (text field)
    - "View All" button text + link (collection picker)
    - Number of product cards (block repeater, admin adds/removes)
    - Each card: product picker (pulls live title/price/image/swatch automatically 
      — no manual price entry to avoid £0.00 bugs)
    - Color scheme picker (to match existing dark theme tokens)
    - Toggle: enable/disable "Quick Add" button
    
    CRITICAL RULE:
    - Price must ALWAYS pull from {{ product.price | money }} or 
      {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }} — 
      never hardcode price values, to prevent the £0.00 display bug seen earlier.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-footwear-picks-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.view_all_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-footwear-picks-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.desktop_columns }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_background }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_border_color }};
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px {{ block.settings.card_hover_glow }};
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 280px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-footwear-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-6px);
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.product_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.product_title_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    min-height: 2.6em;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.price_color }};
    margin: 0;
    transition: text-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-footwear-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px {{ block.settings.price_glow }};
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.swatch_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.swatch_size }}px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.swatch_border_color }};
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-footwear-card-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.15);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px {{ block.settings.swatch_glow }};
  }

  .ai-footwear-quick-add-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.quick_add_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.quick_add_text_color }};
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.quick_add_radius }}px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-footwear-quick-add-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }

  .ai-footwear-quick-add-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.quick_add_hover_bg }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-footwear-picks-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .ai-footwear-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: 200px;
    }

    .ai-footwear-picks-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-footwear-picks-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }

    .ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-width: 160px;
      max-width: 160px;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
    }

    .ai-footwear-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: 140px;
    }

    .ai-footwear-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .ai-footwear-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .ai-footwear-picks-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<footwear-picks-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-footwear-picks-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-footwear-picks-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-footwear-picks-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.section_title != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-footwear-picks-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.section_title }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.view_all_link != blank %}
        <a href="{{ block.settings.view_all_link }}" class="ai-footwear-picks-view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.view_all_text }}
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="ai-footwear-picks-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.products != blank %}
        {% for product in block.settings.products %}
          <div class="ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-footwear-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if product.featured_image %}
                <img
                  src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                  alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                  class="ai-footwear-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="600"
                  height="600"
                >
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-footwear-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-footwear-card-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-footwear-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ product.title }}
              </h3>

              <div class="ai-footwear-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }}
              </div>

              {% assign color_option = product.options_with_values | where: 'name', 'Color' | first %}
              {% if color_option and color_option.values.size > 0 %}
                {% assign first_color = color_option.values.first %}
                <div
                  class="ai-footwear-card-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  style="background-color: {{ first_color | downcase }};"
                  title="{{ first_color }}"
                ></div>
              {% elsif block.settings.default_swatch_color != blank %}
                <div
                  class="ai-footwear-card-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  style="background-color: {{ block.settings.default_swatch_color }};"
                ></div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            {% if block.settings.enable_quick_add %}
              <a
                href="{{ product.url }}"
                class="ai-footwear-quick-add-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ block.settings.quick_add_button_text }}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
        {% for i in (1..4) %}
          <div class="ai-footwear-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-footwear-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-footwear-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ai-footwear-card-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-footwear-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                Product title
              </h3>

              <div class="ai-footwear-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                £0.00
              </div>

              {% if block.settings.default_swatch_color != blank %}
                <div
                  class="ai-footwear-card-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  style="background-color: {{ block.settings.default_swatch_color }};"
                ></div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</footwear-picks-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

